                                        <p><strong>RCA:</strong> <img class="editor-inline-macro"
                                                        src="./Feb2026_files/macro(9)" data-macro-name="jira"
                                                        data-macro-id="ddbe26ef-b7af-4207-9143-ddf82fe6f6ca"
